songs.title: Cash to Burn
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Change if you can do without the things I can't get you
Something  I been countin'-
When's  enough enough bae?
Mink coats, diamond rings and cash for you to burn
The kind of stuff you earn
When's  enough enough bae?
Shit,  I feel like

[Bridge]
Feel like De Nero on Casino
Where  they got the sun up for the C-note
Rings and cash for you to burn
Know I'm shining when you growin' on the ice
The kind of stuff you earn
What  you expect? Me and the girl, she was blowin' on the dice
Run the game, thirty game for the-
Rings and cash for you to burn
The kind of stuff you earn

[Verse]
You can follow some, [?]
[?] you to learn, that you will learn
You can [?] find [?]
[?] you to learn, the nights you done learned
You can take my [?] love [?]
Wave 'em down [?] cash for you to burn
You can take my phone away [?] lock [?]
I'm gon' [?] 'less you gon' learn, 'less you done learned
You can take the [?] up out, fold up, grind back on 'em
[?] you done learned, cash you done burned
You can say what you want, you been lyin'
Know you had 'em [?] you done learned, cash you done burned

[Outro]
Rings and cash for you to burn
The kind of stuff you earn
Rings and cash for you to burn
The kind of stuff you earn
